@host = http://localhost:5123

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Basic Logging
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Log at every level (Debug → Fatal)
GET {{host}}/api/logging/all-levels
Accept: application/json

###

### Log with exception stack trace
GET {{host}}/api/logging/exception
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Diagnostics
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Pipeline health check
GET {{host}}/api/diagnostics/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Clear internal error store
DELETE {{host}}/api/diagnostics/errors
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Routing Demo
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Show routing rules
GET {{host}}/api/routing/rules
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Custom Properties / Structured Logging
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Log with custom properties
GET {{host}}/api/properties/with-scope
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Dynamic File Routing
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Log to tenant-specific file
GET {{host}}/api/dynamic-file/log?tenantId=ACME
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Sensitive Data Masking
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Log with PII (should be masked)
GET {{host}}/api/masking/demo
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Trace API / OpenTelemetry
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create trace span
GET {{host}}/api/trace/span
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### MCP Server (JSON-RPC 2.0)
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Initialize MCP session
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":1,"method":"initialize","params":{}}

###

### List all MCP tools
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":2,"method":"tools/list","params":{}}

###

### Get health status
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":3,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_get_health","arguments":{}}}

###

### Get recent errors
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":4,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_get_errors","arguments":{"count":10}}}

###

### Get sink status
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":5,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_get_sinks","arguments":{}}}

###

### Get configuration
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":6,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_get_config","arguments":{}}}

###

### [NEW v5.2.0] Set log level — change Console to Error+Fatal only
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":7,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_set_log_level","arguments":{"sink":"Console","levels":"Error,Fatal"}}}

###

### [NEW v5.2.0] Search logs — find all entries containing "User"
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":8,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_search_logs","arguments":{"query":"User","count":20}}}

###

### [NEW v5.2.0] Search logs — filter by Warning level
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":9,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_search_logs","arguments":{"level":"Warning"}}}

###

### [NEW v5.2.0] Toggle sink — disable Email sink
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":10,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_toggle_sink","arguments":{"sink":"Email","enabled":false}}}

###

### [NEW v5.2.0] Toggle sink — re-enable Email sink
POST {{host}}/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":11,"method":"tools/call","params":{"name":"loggerhelper_toggle_sink","arguments":{"sink":"Email","enabled":true}}}

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### MCP Demo REST Shortcuts
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### List available MCP tools
GET {{host}}/api/mcp-demo/tools
Accept: application/json

###

### Call get-health via REST
POST {{host}}/api/mcp-demo/call/get-health
Accept: application/json

###

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### Dashboard
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### Open Dashboard UI (open in browser)
GET {{host}}/loggerhelper
Accept: text/html

###

### Dashboard API — status
GET {{host}}/loggerhelper/api/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Dashboard API — recent logs
GET {{host}}/loggerhelper/api/logs
Accept: application/json

###

### Dashboard API — filtered logs (by level)
GET {{host}}/loggerhelper/api/logs?level=Warning
Accept: application/json

###

### Dashboard API — filtered logs (by query)
GET {{host}}/loggerhelper/api/logs?query=Payment
Accept: application/json

###
